INSERT INTO library_unit_build (
                                package_id,
                                target,
                                library_crate_compilation_unit_hash,
                                build_script_compilation_unit_hash,
                                build_script_execution_unit_hash,
                                content_hash
                            ) VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6)
                            RETURNING id AS "id!: i64"
